CatDescriptText: Cutline of image (or 2001.35.29426) published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 18, 1950, pg. 2, reads: "In Carnegie Exhibit - Among the outstanding paintings in the current exhibit at Carnegie Institute is the above landscape mural by Andrew Hooker, talented local artist. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Landscape painting by Andrew W. Hooker hanging in Carnegie Institute (Carnegie Museum of Art)
